1
00:00:23,156 --> 00:00:24,156
Oh, by the way...

2
00:00:24,557 --> 00:00:26,292
About that car accident you had...

3
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:28,495
Where exactly was the injury?

4
00:00:31,865 --> 00:00:33,833
It was a pretty nasty scar.

5
00:00:40,473 --> 00:00:42,542
It must have been so painful.

6
00:00:46,785 --> 00:00:49,215
Why wouldn't you let me come see you?

7
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:51,584
In front of the person I like...

8
00:00:52,585 --> 00:00:54,387
I have to save some face, right?

9
00:01:37,864 --> 00:01:39,666
From the time we were sixteen until now...

10
00:01:41,267 --> 00:01:43,703
No matter who you become,
you don't owe me an answer.

11
00:01:46,873 --> 00:01:48,441
I'll always be right here.
